<p>How to call my static function in twig template without passing through controller?</p>  <p>For example: </p>  <pre><code>... {{ MyStaticClass::getData() }} ... </code></pre>  <p>My Static Class:</p>  <pre><code>class MyStaticClass {     const v1 = 'Value1';     const v2 = 'Value2';     ...      public static function getData() {         ...          return $data;     } } </code></pre>